---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Used & Vintage Goods Fulfillment | Condition Documentation, Authenticity Verification, Full Transparency | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for used goods, vintage items, antiques, collectibles. Condition documentation with photos, authenticity verification, transparency guarantee, 100% insurance, specialized packaging, 24-48 hour delivery.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-vintage.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/'
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴300-₴600'
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Used &amp; Vintage Goods Fulfillment<br />Complete Transparency, Authenticity Verified, Trust-First Handling
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Antiques, vintage items, used goods, pre-owned collectibles. Comprehensive condition documentation with photos, authenticity verification, full transparency, specialized protective packing, 100% insurance, 24-48 hour delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Used & Vintage Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Used & Vintage Goods Need Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📸 Critical Condition Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Each used item is unique. Buyers expect comprehensive documentation: photos from all angles, detailed condition description, defect notation. Documentation is the trust foundation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔍 Authenticity Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Antique items require authenticity expertise and certification. Without documentation, value plummets. Requires expert verification and official authentication certificates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Extreme High Value &amp; Loss Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Antiques worth 50,000+ UAH, vintage goods worth 10,000+ UAH. Loss of single item = major financial impact. Requires maximum security and full insurance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🤝 Buyer Transparency Expectations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Used goods buyers demand complete transparency: full condition history, all defects disclosed, honest assessment. Zero tolerance for misrepresentation or surprise damage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Used & Vintage Item Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Used & vintage retailers sell one-of-a-kind or limited-quantity items. Condition verification is critical. Orders are 1–3 items. Customers expect detailed condition reporting.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Each vintage item is photographed and condition-verified before packing. Descriptions include wear, damage, and authenticity notes. Fragile vintage items are wrapped individually. Presentation respects item value and age.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Vintage item margins are 50–100% but customer disputes over condition reduce net profit. Our detailed photography and condition verification prevent disputes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>5,000+ vintage item orders processed, 12+ vintage retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Used & Vintage Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Comprehensive Condition Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Multi-angle photography from all sides. Detailed written condition assessment. Defect notation with locations. Complete documentation package with buyer transparency guarantee.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Authenticity Verification &amp; Certification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Expert authentication for antique items. Official certification documents. Provenance documentation where available. Eliminates buyer doubt about value and authenticity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Secure Storage &amp; Specialized Packing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">High-value items stored separately with security protocols. Custom protective packing per item type (fragile antiques, delicate vintage clothing, etc.). Maximum protection from handling damage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Specialist Courier Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Premium antiques via specialized high-value courier. GPS tracking with real-time updates. Photos before/after delivery. Chain-of-custody documentation. White-glove service.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Used & Vintage Goods</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Documentation &amp; Specialized Delivery</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Picking &amp; inspection per order</span>
            <span class="font-bold">40–80 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Condition documentation &amp; photography per item</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–150 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Authenticity verification (optional)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">200–500 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized protective packing</span>
            <span class="font-bold">30–100 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialist courier delivery (up to 50km)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">150–400 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Antique Shop Fulfillment (40 orders/month)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Picking &amp; inspection: 40 × 60 = 2,400 UAH<br/>
          Documentation &amp; photos: 40 × 100 = 4,000 UAH<br/>
          Specialized delivery: 40 × 275 = 11,000 UAH<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 17,400 UAH/month = 435 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: multi-angle documentation, condition assessment, specialized packing, courier delivery, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Trust &amp; Authenticity Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Condition Documentation</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Multi-angle photos, detailed assessment</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">Expert</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Authenticity Verification</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Certified, documented provenance</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Loss Insurance</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Immediate compensation guaranteed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Scale Your Antiques & Vintage Platform?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        100% transparency, complete documentation, expert authenticity verification, specialized protective handling, 100% insurance, specialized courier delivery. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
